Text:
This version have some gun/bow sound bugs, you should uninstall a mod and install a new version:

http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7517389/DarthMod__Shogun_II_v4.2___%28TwoPlus%29

or you can find a fix here:

www.twcenter.net/forums/showthread.php?t=555776

Keep in mind, that you should have latest version installed, in order to find more multiplayer games.
